==Introduction==
主砲等から発射される落下傘付の照明弾です。<br>
夜戦時において敵艦隊付近を照明し、味方艦隊の夜間攻撃を支援します(敵艦隊の夜間特殊攻撃発生も少し抑えることが可能です)。

''The Star Shell is a parachute flare fired from the ship's cannons.''<br>
''It can illuminate the enemy fleet's position which can aid any allied ships' attacks on the enemy. (It can also lower the offensive capabilities of the enemy fleet.)''

==Notes==
*Chance to provide all of the following effects when a ship equipped with this enters a night battle:
:*[[File:Flare_Seaplane_2.jpg|thumb|220px|Star Shell during activation]]Night battle attack accuracy of your fleet increases.
:*Special attack rate of your fleet increases.
:*Special attack rate of the enemy fleet decreases.
*Activation rate is not 100%; multiple ''ships'' equipped with star shells will increase the chance of activation.
*There is no side effects associated with star shell, unlike [[Searchlight]].
*Effect can be stacked with [[Searchlight]].

